GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/date/2025-01-11

### Get Order by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{{orderId}}

### Create Order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Nguyễn Văn A",
  "customerPhone": "0123456789",
  "customerTable": "Bàn 1",
  "notes": "Không cay",
  "paymentMethod": "CASH",
  "paymentStatus": "SUCCESS",
  "orderCreator": "STAFF",
  "orderCreatorName": "Nhân viên",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "{{productId}}",
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 25000,
      "subtotal": 50000,
      "selectedSize": "Lớn",
      "selectedToppings": ["Sữa"],
      "note": "Ít đá"
    }
  ]
}

### Update Order Status
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}

